@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1) 회원가입 성공
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "error-test-user",
  "password": "password1234"
}

### 2) 회원가입 중복 에러 확인
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "error-test-user",
  "password": "password1234"
}

### 3) 로그인 인증 실패 확인
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "error-test-user",
  "password": "wrong-password"
}

### 4) ValidationPipe 에러 확인
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": 123,
  "password": ""
}
